        <:props_panel>
          <.custom_search class="mb-16" />
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg lg:text-2xl font-bold">Table Content Component Props</h2>

            <.custom_table id="table-content-component-table">
              <:header>
                <.table_th>Name</.table_th>

                <.table_th>Type</.table_th>

                <.table_th>Required</.table_th>

                <.table_th>Description</.table_th>
              </:header>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>id</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  A unique identifier used to manage state and interaction. Default is <strong>nil</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>class</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  Custom CSS class for additional styling. Default is <strong>nil</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>title</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  Specifies the title of the element. Default is <strong>nil</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>variant</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  Determines the style of the table of content. Supported values: <strong>default</strong>, <strong>outline</strong>, <strong>transparent</strong>, <strong>shadow</strong>, <strong>bordered</strong>, <strong>gradient</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>color</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  Determines the color theme of the table of content. Supported values: <strong>natural</strong>, <strong>primary</strong>, <strong>secondary</strong>, <strong>success</strong>, <strong>warning</strong>, <strong>danger</strong>, <strong>info</strong>, <strong>silver</strong>, <strong>misc</strong>, <strong>dawn</strong>. Default is <strong>natural</strong>.The
                  <strong>default</strong>
                  and <strong>bordered</strong>
                  variants have extra color options: <strong>dark</strong>
                  and <strong>white</strong>, which in both light mode and dark mode, these colors are always the same.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>space</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>Space between items. Default is <strong>nil</strong>.</.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>animated</.table_td>

                <.table_td>boolean</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  This adds a class to the HTML body for smooth scrolling. Default is <strong>false</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>padding</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  Determines padding for items. Default is <strong>nil</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>item</.table_td>

                <.table_td>Slot</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  The slot name is used to specify a named placeholder in the component. It allows the component to accept custom content for rendering. The available props for this slot are: <strong>class</strong>: Custom CSS class for additional styling, <strong>title</strong>: Specifies the title of the element, <strong>title_class</strong>: Custom CSS class for additional styling to title, <strong>wrapper_class</strong>: Custom CSS class for additional styling to content wrapper, <strong>content_class</strong>: Custom CSS class for additional styling to content, <strong>link_class</strong>: Custom CSS class for additional styling to link, <strong>icon</strong>: Icon displayed alongside the item, <strong>icon_class</strong>: Custom class for the icon, <strong>font_weight</strong>: Custom class for the font weight, <strong>link_title</strong>: Determines the title of the link, <strong>link</strong>: Determines the link URL, <strong>active</strong>: Indicates whether the element is currently active and visible.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>rounded</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  Determines the border radius. Default is <strong>nil</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>border</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  Determines border style. Default is <strong>extra_small</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>

              <:row>
                <.table_td>size</.table_td>

                <.table_td>string</.table_td>

                <.table_td>No</.table_td>

                <.table_td>
                  Determines the overall size of the elements, including padding and font size. Default is <strong>small</strong>.
                </.table_td>
              </:row>
            </.custom_table>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-8 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg lg:text-2xl font-bold">Content Wrapper Component Props</h2>

            <.custom_table id="content-wrapper-component-table">
